#: contributing/communication.rst:2
msgid "Weblate Contributor Communication Guidelines"
msgstr "Riktlinjer fГ¶r kommunikation mellan Weblate-bidragare"

#: contributing/communication.rst:5
msgid "GitHub Issues"
msgstr "GitHub-problem"

#: contributing/communication.rst:6
msgid ""
"`GitHub Issues <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/issues>`_ is where "
"bugs can be reported, and features can be requested. Issue submission form "
"provides templates for each to simplify issue creation, and review and "
"implementation process; it also guides to other places with information like "
"documentation, Discussions, HackerOne program, and Weblate Care."
msgstr ""
"`GitHub Issues <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/issues>`_ ГӨr dГӨr "
"buggar kan rapporteras och funktioner kan begГӨras. FormulГӨret fГ¶r att skicka "
"in ГӨrenden innehГҘller mallar fГ¶r varje ГӨrende fГ¶r att fГ¶renkla skapandet av "
"ГӨrenden samt gransknings- och implementeringsprocessen. Det innehГҘller ocksГҘ "
"lГӨnkar till andra platser med information, sГҘsom dokumentation, "
"diskussioner, HackerOne-programmet och Weblate Care."

#: contributing/communication.rst:11
