"`GitHub Discussions <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/discussions>`_ ГӨr "
"en communityplats. NГӨr du publicerar nГҘgot dГӨr kan du vГӨlja mellan "
"kategorierna IdГ©er, OmrГ¶stningar, FrГҘgor och svar samt Visa och berГӨtta. "
"Kategorin AllmГӨnt passar alla inlГӨgg som inte passar in i de andra "
"kategorierna. Medlemmarna i Weblate-teamet besГ¶ker ibland Discussions och "
"kan ocksГҘ nГӨmnas med sina GitHub-anvГӨndarnamn."

#: contributing/communication.rst:18
msgid "Weblate on Mastodon"
msgstr "Weblate pГҘ Mastodon"

#: contributing/communication.rst:19
msgid ""
"If you want to attract a wide community of Weblate users, fans, and "
"developers to your case, you can follow and mention `@weblate@fosstodon.org "
