"korrigeras, sГҘ att alla ГӨndringar kan tillГӨmpas selektivt av underhГҘllaren "
"eller andra berГ¶rda parter."

#: contributing/snippets/code-guide.rst:35
msgid ""
"Furthermore, separate changes enable bisecting much better for tracking "
"issues and regression in the future."
