"sprГҘk och domГӨner som behГ¶vs. FГ¶rtydliga hur Г¶versГӨttningsbackenden fungerar "
"och vilken kvalitet efterredigeraren kan fГ¶rvГӨnta sig."

#: devel/community.rst:30
msgid "Review translations"
msgstr "Granska Г¶versГӨttningar"

#: devel/community.rst:31
msgid ""
"The translations should be reviewed by a second person after the post-"
"editing. With an impartial and competent reviewer, the two people rule "
"reduces the errors and improves the quality and consistency of the content. "
"Providing reviewers with previews or alpha translations will make for the "
"best review. Screenshots, explanations also help to review the strings in "
