#: formats.rst:42
msgid ""
"Both :index:`monolingual <pair: translation; monolingual>` "
"and :index:`bilingual <pair: translation; bilingual>` formats are supported. "
"Bilingual formats store two languages in single fileвҖ”source and translation "
"(typical examples are :ref:`gettext`, :ref:`xliff` or :ref:`apple`). On the "
"other side, monolingual formats identify the string by ID, and each language "
"file contains only the mapping of those to any given language "
"(typically :ref:`aresource`). Some file formats are used in both variants, "
"see the detailed description below."
msgstr ""
"BГҘde :index:`monolingual <pair: translation; monolingual>` "
"och :index:`bilingual <pair: translation; bilingual>` format stГ¶ds. "
"TvГҘsprГҘkiga format lagrar tvГҘ sprГҘk i en enda fil вҖ“ kГӨllsprГҘk och "
"Г¶versГӨttning (typiska exempel ГӨr :ref:`gettext`, :ref:`xliff` "
"eller :ref:`apple`). Г… andra sidan identifierar ensprГҘkiga format strГӨngen "
"med hjГӨlp av ID, och varje sprГҘkfil innehГҘller endast mappningen av dessa "
"till ett visst sprГҘk (vanligtvis :ref:`aresource`). Vissa filformat anvГӨnds "
"i bГҘda varianterna, se den detaljerade beskrivningen nedan."

#: formats.rst:50
msgid ""
"For correct use of monolingual files, Weblate requires access to a file "
"containing complete list of strings to translate with their sourceвҖ”this file "
"is called :ref:`component-template` within Weblate, though the naming might "
"vary in your paradigm."
msgstr ""
"FГ¶r korrekt anvГӨndning av ensprГҘkiga filer krГӨver Weblate ГҘtkomst till en "
"fil som innehГҘller en komplett lista Г¶ver strГӨngar som ska Г¶versГӨttas med "
"deras kГӨlla. Denna fil kallas :ref:`component-template` inom Weblate, men "
"namnet kan variera beroende pГҘ ditt paradigm."

#: formats.rst:55
msgid ""
"Additionally this workflow can be extended by utilizing :ref:`component-"
"intermediate` to include strings provided by developers, but not to be used "
"as is in the final strings."
msgstr ""
"Dessutom kan detta arbetsflГ¶de utГ¶kas genom att anvГӨnda :ref:`component-"
"intermediate` fГ¶r att inkludera strГӨngar som tillhandahГҘlls av utvecklare, "
"men som inte ska anvГӨndas som de ГӨr i de slutliga strГӨngarna."

#: formats.rst:62
msgid "String states"
