"i18n-json`, :ref:`gotext-json`, :ref:`arb`, :ref:`dotnet`). MГҘnga andra "
"format extraherar nГӨrmaste kommentar som kГӨllstrГӨngbeskrivning."

#: formats.rst:86
msgid ""
"The :ref:`additional-explanation` on strings can be stored and parsed from a "
"few file formats."
