"fГ¶rstГҘ hur strГӨngen anvГӨnds."

#: formats.rst:99
msgid ""
"This information is typically available in bilingual formats where strings "
"are extracted from the source code using tools. For example :ref:`gettext` "
"and :ref:`qtling`."
msgstr ""
"Denna information finns vanligtvis tillgГӨnglig i tvГҘsprГҘkiga format dГӨr "
"strГӨngar extraheras frГҘn kГӨllkoden med hjГӨlp av verktyg. Till "
"exempel :ref:`gettext` och :ref:`qtling`."

#: formats.rst:107
msgid ""
"Translation flags allow customizing Weblate behavior. Some formats support "
"defining those in the translation file (you can always define them in the "
"Weblate interface, see :ref:`custom-checks`)."
msgstr ""
"Г–versГӨttningsflaggor gГ¶r det mГ¶jligt att anpassa Weblates beteende. Vissa "
"format stГ¶der definition av dessa i Г¶versГӨttningsfilen (du kan alltid "
"definiera dem i Weblate-grГӨnssnittet, se :ref:`custom-checks`)."

#: formats.rst:111
msgid "This feature is modelled on flags in :ref:`gettext`."
