"FГ¶r ensprГҘkiga format kan strГӨngidentifieraren (ofta kallad nyckel) tjГӨna "
"samma syfte och ytterligare kontext ГӨr inte nГ¶dvГӨndig."

#: formats.rst:142
msgid "Pluralized strings"
msgstr "Pluraliserade strГӨngar"

#: formats.rst:144
msgid ""
"Plurals are necessary to properly localize strings with variable count. The "
"rules depend on a target language and many formats follow CLDR specification "
"for that."
