"translation``, ``needs-adaptation``, ``needs-l10n``). Om attributet "
"``state`` saknas betraktas en strГӨng som Г¶versatt sГҘ snart ett ``<target>``-"
"element finns."

#: formats/xliff.rst:51
msgid ""
"If the translation string has ``approved=\"yes\"``, it will also be imported "
