"Alla kontrolltecken och ledande och efterfГ¶ljande blanktecken tas bort."

#: user/glossary.rst:155
msgid ":ref:`glossary-forbidden` are skipped."
msgstr ":ref:`glossary-forbidden` hoppas Г¶ver."

#: user/glossary.rst:159
msgid ""
"Many services store glossaries server-side and enforce limit on the number "
